{{Quote|Hey Imp! I call this the "wing-tip"!|Wedge Antilles|<ref name="X-Wing Rogue Squadron 1">[[X-Wing Rogue Squadron 1|''X-Wing Rogue Squadron'' 1]]</ref>}}
The '''wing tip''' was a maneuver utilized by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron's]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] during a dogfight over the planet [[Cilpar]] in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]].

Getting in close behind an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE fighter]], he used the starboard [[S-foils/Legends|S-foils]] of his [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing]] to shear off the port wing of the enemy fighter, sending it slamming into the ground.

